title: Aju Vegan Bistro
description: Vegetable Kitchen Bar Aju became all-vegan July 2013. This space in Nakazakicho area with local izakaya feel, offers dishes such as vege Korean pork'n kimchi, soy chicken, and vege shrimp fries. Uses organic ingredients. Menu items are accompanied by photos. Has menu in Chinese. At lunch time, lunch box or burgers only. Cafe time Tue-Fri 2:30-5pm for organic coffee and cake. At 大阪市北区中崎町, subway (purple line) Nakazakicho exit 1, go through the shopping arcade for 50m, at dnail salon turn left, you'll find a signboard. Moved behind current building, with more space, and small vegan shop with raw sweets, Oct 2015.
